title: The navigation application on my mobile phone cannot receive signals from GPS satellites. What can I do?
answer:
Take your mobile phone to an area with better signal strength..


	Check the **Location services **settings. If only **GPS satellites** is selected, this problem may occur when you are in a built-up area. To solve this problem, take your mobile phone to an open area. You may have to try for several times before your mobile phone receives signals from GPS satellites.
